manifest_analysis.title:
Application Data can be Backed up
[android:allowBackup] flag is missing.
manifest_analysis.desc: The flag [android:allowBackup] should be set to false. By default it is set to true and allows anyone to backup your application data via adb. It allows users who have enabled USB debugging to copy application data off of the device.
manifest_analysis.name: Application Data can be Backed up [android:allowBackup] flag is missing.

nx.description: The shared object has NX bit set. This marks a memory page non-executable making attacker injected shellcode non-executable.

stack_canary.description: This shared object has a stack canary value added to the stack so that it will be overwritten by a stack buffer that overflows the return address. This allows detection of overflows by verifying the integrity of the canary before function return.

relocation_readonly.description: This shared object has full RELRO enabled. RELRO ensures that the GOT cannot be overwritten in vulnerable ELF binaries. In Full RELRO, the entire GOT (.got and .got.plt both) is marked as read-only.

rpath.description: The shared object does not have run-time search path or RPATH set.

runpath.description: The shared object does not have RUNPATH set.

fortify.description: The shared object does not have any fortified functions. Fortified functions provides buffer overflow checks against glibc's commons insecure functions like strcpy, gets etc. Use the compiler option -D_FORTIFY_SOURCE=2 to fortify functions.

nx.description: The shared object does not have NX bit set. NX bit offer protection against exploitation of memory corruption vulnerabilities by marking memory page as non-executable. Use option --noexecstack or -z noexecstack to mark stack as non executable.

stack_canary.description: This shared object does not have a stack canary value added to the stack. Stack canaries are used to detect and prevent exploits from overwriting return address. Use the option -fstack-protector-all to enable stack canaries.

relocation_readonly.description: This shared object does not have RELRO enabled. The entire GOT (.got and .got.plt both) are writable. Without this compiler flag, buffer overflows on a global variable can overwrite GOT entries. Use the option -z,relro,-z,now to enable full RELRO and only -z,relro to enable partial RELRO.

How to get cryptocurrency without risk !

Do you know the best way to buy and sell cryptocurrency? 

Do you know which cryptocurrency exchange is best?

CryptoRabbt is A New Free Tool to Help You Save Money and Get Free Cryptocurrency Without Risk.

- Find the best price across exchanges!
- Find arbitrage opportunities!
- Try your strategy with a demo trading mode without an real account!
- Try your strategy with a real trading mode from the app!

We can easily compare cryptocurrency prices across multiple exchanges. 

Just push the buy and sell button!
We can automatically buy and sell at the best price.

Are you under the impression that you can buy cryptocurrency at the same price everywhere? 


It's easy to install and uninstall this tool. 
It's easy to create your new account. 

You will only need a email address and few minutes. 
Try it's free!! 

Help! 
I'm sorry that my English isn't very good. 
Could somebody give me checking my English?

There are four benefit. 
------------------------------------------------------------ 
1 We can save money more easily. 
Because we can easily find the lowest price to buy or the highest price to sell. 

2 We can make money more easily. 
Because we can easily find arbitrage opportunities. 

3 We can try our strategy without risk on demo trading. 
You don't need to have an real account.

4 We can buy and sell cryptocurrency from the app. 
15 order a week in this Free version.

They are free! 1/11/2019

3 Set public and private API keys for this app. 

This is not necessary. 
You can buy and sell directly from the official website. 
------------------------------------------------------------ 


What is arbitrage? 
As a simple strategy, arbitrage is to buy and sell simultaneously on two exchanges. 
For example, when Alice's exchange buy price is 100 and Bob's exchange sell price is 101, 
we can earn 1 by buy and sell simultaneously. 

Are you under the impression that you can buy cryptocurrency at the same price everywhere? 
The truth is different, even for the same cryptocurrency, the price varies depending on the exchange. 

The basic way to do arbitrage. 
1 Buy cryptocurrency. --buy 100 
2 Send cryptocurrency to another exchange. --send Alice's exchange to Bob's exchange 
3 Sell cryptocurrency. --sell 101 

But it will take many time to sent cryptocurrency. 
How to avoid time lag? 

The more complicated way to do arbitrage. 
1 Buy cryptocurrency. --buy 100

3 Send cryptocurrency to another exchange. --send Alice's exchange to Bob's exchange 

To use this tool we can know these opportunity by text , sound and vibrate. 
Try it's free!! 

We recommend checking for a different version according to the purpose. 
---------------------- 
1 CryptoRabbit Lite version : only getting info 
2 CryptoRabbit Normal version : demo trading 
3 CryptoRabbit Plus version : real trading -> currently under development! 
---------------------- 


Currently, this app supports the following exchanges: 
------------- 
binance

coinbene 
------------- 
Could you recommend any other nice exchanges? 

1 Low trading Fees. 
Because we can save more money. 

---trading fees 9/8/2019 --- 
binance 0.0075%

coinbene 0.005% 

2 Only need an email address 
Because Cryptocurrency has no boundaries in the world 
and not everyone in the world has a passport or driver's license. 

3 Affiliate Program. 
Because I become happy. 

Hitbtc has no Affiliate Program . 
I'm sad. :_( 

Could you recommend any other nice exchanges?

Try it's free!!
